#doctors_english
@Mr.Kapoor
Good morning, Dr. Sharma!
@Dr.Sharma
Good morning! What’s wrong with you?
@Mr.Kapoor
I have been suffering from fever since yesterday.
@Dr.Sharma
Do you have any other symptoms?
@Mr.Kapoor
I also feel headache and shivering.
@Dr.Sharma
Let me see your temperature in your health report.
At this time the fever is 102 degree. Don’t worry, there is nothing serious.
I am giving you the medicine, and you will be all right in couple of days.
@Mr.Kapoor
Thank you, doctor.
@Dr.Sharma
But get your blood tested for malaria, and come back tomorrow.
@Mr.Kapoor
OK doctor.
@Dr.Sharma
I shall recommend at least two days rest for you. And some medicine to relive your pain.
@Mr.Kapoor
Thank you very much.
Please tell me how shall I take this medicine?
@Dr.Sharma
This medicine is for two days only.
Take this dose as soon as you your get in bed before sleeping.
@Mr.Kapoor
What should I eat doctor?
@Dr.Sharma
You should eat only light food. You can take milk and fresh fruit also.
@Mr.Kapoor
Thanks doctor.
@Dr.Sharma
It’s all right.
@Mr.Kapoor
Thank you doctor. I shall see you tomorrow with my blood report

